description: Enjoy your sun drenched one bedroom in the heart of the vibrant Fort Point neighborhood. The 572 sq ft condo features 14 ft ceilings, 3 extra large windows, a walk in closet, and laundry in the unit. The premier layout makes this unit feel larger than it's square footage. All the original charm was preserved including exposed brick and original wood beams making this a quintessential Boston unit. High end finishes throughout; Bosch appliances, polished chrome fixtures, and dark wide plank hardwood floors that create a distinctive, contemporary urban feel. Seller added custom upgrades including window treatments, a sliding bedroom door, and primary closet build out. Additional highlights include a large common roof deck with grills, deeded basement storage unit, common bike storage, and heat/hot water included in condo fee. Steps to the Seaport, Downtown and some of the best restaurants in Boston.
